MEASUREMENTS. Total length 4.06. Prosoma 2.13 long, 1.66 wide; opisthosoma 2.29 long, 1.53 wide. Prosoma brown, with longitudinal dark brown band. Cervical grooves distinct, radial furrows indistinct (
Fig. 1A
). Eye sizes and interdistances: AME 0.14, ALE 0.16, PME 0.17, PLE 0.15; AME–AME 0.09, AME–ALE 0.11, PME–PME 0.08, PME–PLE 0.14, ALE–PLE 0.03. MOA anterior width 0.37, posterior width 0.41, length 0.42. Clypeus 0.10 high.

OPISTHOSOMA. Oval, with two pairs of sigillae. Both dorsum and venter yellowish brown, with black markings (
